lead_paragraph: England all-rounder Ben Stokes has been ruled out of the third test against Pakistan with the calf injury he sustained in the second test, the England and Wales Cricket Board (ECB) said on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Calf Injury Rules England's Stokes Out of Third Test
